<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/359020-a-4th-grade-student-asked-me-about-this">A 4th grade student asked me about this book. I tried to find information on reading level, but couldn&#39;t. Is the content appropriate for elementary students? How difficult is the vocabulary?</a>
</div>
